title: Mario 3 & The Wizard Reboot
description: Plante ditches the rest of the gang, leaving them with an ancient game that came out around the dawn of time. (Thankfully it was pretty good.) The remaining gang try to reboot the 1989 film, The Wizard, for a new generation.
author: thebestiesbizemail@gmail.com (The Besties)
